      "text": "រំពេចនោះស្រាប់តែកង្ហែនឃើញពោតមួយជ្រុះនៅលើដី វាលាន់មាត់និយាយថា៖ “ អូ! ពោតមួយនេះទុំល្អណាស់"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2f77f55328-43f0-4e3c-be63-f44aa5441ba5%2f%e1%9f%a2%e1%9f%a1%e1%9e%81+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%80%e1%9f%92%e1%9e%9a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%99%e1%9f%92%e1%9e%9f%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%80%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%9b%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%94%e1%9f%81%e1%9e%9b%2fimage4.png",
      "text": "កង្ហែនថា៖ ​“យកវាមកស៊ីសិន ថ្ងៃនេះខ្ញុំហេងណាស់បានចំណីស៊ី”។"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2f77f55328-43f0-4e3c-be63-f44aa5441ba5%2f%e1%9f%a2%e1%9f%a1%e1%9e%81+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%80%e1%9f%92%e1%9e%9a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%99%e1%9f%92%e1%9e%9f%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%80%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%9b%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%94%e1%9f%81%e1%9e%9b%2fimage5.png",
      "text": "ថ្ងៃនោះជាថ្ងៃបេលចាំមើលចំការ បេលគិតថា៖ “ខ្ញុំទៅមើលចំការពោតសិន ក្រែងមានសត្វអីស៊ី”។"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2f77f55328-43f0-4e3c-be63-f44aa5441ba5%2f%e1%9f%a2%e1%9f%a1%e1%9e%81+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%80%e1%9f%92%e1%9e%9a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%99%e1%9f%92%e1%9e%9f%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%80%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%9b%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%94%e1%9f%81%e1%9e%9b%2fimage6.png",
      "text": "មកដល់កៀនចំការពោត បេលប្រទះឃើញកង្ហែនមួយដែលកំពុងតែស៊ីពោតនៅនឹងដី បេលនិយាយ៖ “អូ! គឺឯងទេដែលលួចស៊ីពោតយើង តាំងពីថ្ងៃមុនមកថ្ងៃនេះ”។"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2f77f55328-43f0-4e3c-be63-f44aa5441ba5%2f%e1%9f%a2%e1%9f%a1%e1%9e%81+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%80%e1%9f%92%e1%9e%9a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%99%e1%9f%92%e1%9e%9f%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%80%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%9b%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%94%e1%9f%81%e1%9e%9b%2fimage7.png",
      "text": "បេលខឹងក៏ដេញវាយកង្ហែននោះ។"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/todd_bequette%40sil.org%2f77f55328-43f0-4e3c-be63-f44aa5441ba5%2f%e1%9f%a2%e1%9f%a1%e1%9e%81+%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%a2%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%93+%e1%9e%80%e1%9f%92%e1%9e%9a%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%99%e1%9f%92%e1%9e%9f%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%80%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%9b%e2%80%8b%e1%9e%94%e1%9f%81%e1%9e%9b%2fimage8.png",
      "text": "កង្ហែនរត់គេចពីបេលចូលក្នុងព្រៃ ដោយនិយាយថា៖ “ឯងមិនបាច់ដេញវាយអញទេ ឯងដេញអញមិនទាន់ដែរ”។"
    },
